                <tr><td class="help">
                    <a id="a1" name="a1"></a>&nbsp;How to Register?
                </td></tr>
                <tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>
                    <div style="text-align:justify;">
                        Before you start shopping, you need to register yourself with us and give us information
                        that will allow us to communicate with you regarding your transactions. Registration
                        is very easy with <strong>SV Shopping</strong>. Three of our sections i.e. Shopping
                        Cart, Shopping List and My Account are password protected. When you click on any
                        of these links you will reach a sign in page. A new user can register here or members
                        can login to their account directly.
                    </div>
                </td></tr>
