                        to protect your credit card information. You can place your orders using Netscape's
                        SSL encryption (the Internet standard for secure transactions). In fact, shopping
                        online with a credit card at <strong>SV Shopping</strong> is even safer than using
                        a credit card at a restaurant because we do not retain your credit card information.
