                        </p>
                    </div>
                </td></tr>
                <tr><td valign="top" align="right"><a href="help.aspx#" >Top</a></td></tr>
             <tr><td class="help">
                    <a id="a6" name="a6"></a>&nbsp;How to protect your privacy online?
                </td></tr>
                <tr><td valign="top" align="left"><div style="text-align:justify;">&nbsp;</div></td></tr>
                <tr><td valign="top" align="left">
                    <div style="text-align:justify;">
                        Never give your password to anyone online. Make your password at least eight characters
                        in length and a maximum of 20. Create a password that includes a combination of
                        numbers and letters. If you have fallen for an online scam and gave out your password,
                        change your password right away. You can do this by entering the 'My Account' section
                        and Modifying User Information. Once you have finished surfing through <strong>SV Shopping.com</strong>,
                        do not leave the website open. The only way to log off from the site is to close
                        the window.
                    </div>
                </td></tr>
                <tr><td valign="top" align="right"><a href="help.aspx#">Top</a></td></tr>
             <tr><td class="help">
                    <a id="a7" name="a7"></a>&nbsp;About Personal Details
                </td></tr>
                <tr><td valign="top" align="left"><div style="text-align:justify;">&nbsp;</div></td></tr>
                <tr><td valign="top" align="left">
                    <div style="text-align:justify;">
                        You can modify the personal Details (e-mail address, phone numbers, password), shipping
                        information, billing details;. Just log into your account and click on ?Modify User
                        Information? in My Account. The password must have at least 8 characters and a maximum
                        of 20.It is also case-sensitive.
                        <p>
                            Forgot Password-If you have forgotten your password, then click on Shopping Cart
                            or Shopping List or My Account and you will reach the Login page where there is
                            a link to ?Forgot Your Password? ? You must remember your User Name and on entering
                            that, you will be taken to your hint question. On answering the Hint Question in
                            exactly the same words as you had entered during the Registration process ,you would
                            be shown your password.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </td></tr>
                <tr><td valign="top" align="right"><a href="help.aspx#" >Top</a></td></tr>
             <tr><td class="help">
                    <a id="a8" name="a8"></a>&nbsp;How to View your Shopping Cart?
                </td></tr>
                <tr><td valign="top" align="left"><div style="text-align:justify;">&nbsp;</div></td></tr>
                <tr><td valign="top" align="left">
                    <div style="text-align:justify;">
                        Once you have registered with us and logged into your account, you can click on
                        Shopping Cart from any page and you can check on all the items you had put in there.
                        You can also remove an item by deleting it totally or adding it to your Shopping
                        List for later purchases. Incase you are happy with what you currently have in the
                        Shopping Cart then click on the 'Check Out' button or browse through the site some
                        more by clicking on the 'Continue Shopping' button. You can select the person to
                        whom you wish to send the items. All you need to do is to select the name of the
                        person (alias) whom you want to send that particular product and click on the update
                        button. Incase you wish to add a new address, please click on 'add new address'
                        and fill in the details in the subsequent page.
                        <p>
                            You can also change the quantity of the product, which you have selected to buy.
                            All you need to do is to fill the desired quantity in the appropriate box and click
                            update to register your change.
                        </p>
                        </div>
                    </td></tr>
                    <tr><td valign="top" align="right"><a href="help.aspx#" >Top</a></td></tr>
