                            purse strings don't allow you to. In this case, just put it in your Shopping List
                            and next time when you have received your pocket money or your salary or some money
                            from your aunt just go to the Shopping List and indulge. Also, you might want to
                            send a gift directly to a friend whose birthday is probably a month later. So, if
                            you come across the perfect product for him/her just add it to your Shopping List
                            and log on a week or two before and add it to your Shopping Cart directly.
